Package teal.sim.engine

Provides class that define and support the TEALsim simulation engine (SimEngine).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HasEngine
    Provides for any object which is directly controled through the SimEngine.
    HasEngineControl  
    HasSimEngine
    Provides for any object which is directly controled through the SimEngine.
    TEngine
    The TEngine provides the minimum interface for a simulation including both the simulated objects and forces that make up the world and provide an interface to the renders that model the results.
    TEngineControl
    EngineControl objects are the primary means through which the application, and its user, control the model.
